text:
Stylus styles to make torch docs fit on one page below. Many times I have missed something important because scrolled out of view.

table{ table-layout:fixed; }
td:nth-child(1), th:nth-child(1) { width: 15rem; }
article.pytorch-article p { margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; }
article.pytorch-article .wy-table-responsive table tbody td { padding: 0; }

