&lt;|tool_calls_section_begin|&gt;
&lt;|tool_call_begin|&gt;functions.get_weather:0&lt;|tool_call_argument_begin|&gt;{"location": "shanghai"}&lt;|tool_call_end|&gt;
&lt;|tool_calls_section_end|&gt;

vs shell:

$ getweather shanghai

